The paper discusses recommendation systems for different Document Networks (DN) such as the World Wide Web (WWW), Digital Libraries, or Scientific Databases, which are all related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data mining (cs.SI). The paper also talks about distance functions and associative networks, which are relevant to graph theory (cs.DL) and social networks (cs.SD). Additionally, the paper discusses algorithms and models, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG).
